#~ msgid "&konqueror; Basics"
#~ msgstr "&konqueror; Osnove"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Like all &kde; applications, &konqueror; is highly configurable. This "
#~ "document describes how &konqueror; behaves with the normal, default "
#~ "settings."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kao i sve &kde; aplikacije, &konqueror; je veoma prilagodljiv. Ovaj "
#~ "dokument opisuje kako se &konqueror; ponaša sa normalnim, početnim "
#~ "opcijama."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A three button mouse can be useful when you are running &konqueror; or "
#~ "any other &kde; application. If your mouse only has two buttons then you "
#~ "should be able to set your system up so that you can simulate a &MMB; by "
#~ "pressing both buttons at the same time."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Miš sa tri tipke može biti koristan kada koristite &konqueror; ili bilo "
#~ "koju drugu &kde; aplikaciju. Ako vaš miš ima dvije tipke onda bi ste "
#~ "trebali moći podesiti vaš sistem tako da možete simulirati &MMB; "
#~ "pritiskom obje tipke u isto vrijeme."

#~ msgid "You can read more about mouse usage in <xref linkend=\"lmb-mmb\"/>"
#~ msgstr "Više o upotrebi miša možete pročitati u <xref linkend=\"lmb-mmb\"/>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you are used to having to double-click to perform an action, then take "
#~ "care, because in common with the rest of &kde;, &konqueror; defaults to "
#~ "single-clicking."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako ste navikli na dvo-klik da izvedete neku akciju, budite oprezni, jer "
#~ "kao i u ostatku &kde; &konqueror; je po osnovi orijentiran ka jednom "
#~ "kliku."

#~ msgid "Starting &konqueror;"
#~ msgstr "Pokretanje &konqueror;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Being a combined File Manager and Browser, &konqueror; will automatically "
#~ "switch between the two modes as needed when it is running, but it is "
#~ "convenient to be able to choose which mode is to be used when you start "
#~ "it up."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Budući da je kombinirani upravitelj datotekama i pretraživač, &konqueror; "
#~ "će automatski prelaziti iz jednog moda u drugi kada radi, ali je zgodno "
#~ "što se može odabrati u kojem obliku će se koristiti kada se pokrene."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "From the application launcher menu, select "
#~ "<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Internet</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Konqueror (Web "
#~ "Browser)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to start it as a browser."
