#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can move it to the <filename>Trash</filename> folder, which is the "
#~ "safest method as you can get it back if you realize that you have made a "
#~ "mistake."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete ih premjestiti u <filename>Trash</filename> folder, što je "
#~ "najsigurniji metod pošto ih možete vratiti ako ste napravili pogrešku."

