#~ "<quote><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></quote> and "
#~ "<quote><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem></quote> options."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ili, ako imate <quote>označenu</quote> stavku, meni "
