#~ "<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or by moving the mouse pointer to "
#~ "a clear area of the window and holding the &RMB; down to bring up a menu "
#~ "containing the <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> option."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Dođite u folder u koji želite kopirati stavku onda umetnite stavku u novi "
#~ "folder korištenjem alatne trake <guiicon>Umetni</guiicon>  dugmeta ili "
#~ "meni trake <menuchoice><guimenu>Izmjeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Umetni</"
#~ "guimenuitem></menuchoice> opciju ili <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#~ "<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> kombinaciju tipki, ili pomaknite pokazivač "
#~ "miša na slobodan prostor prozora i pritisnite  &RMB; da prikažete meni "
#~ "koji sadrži <guimenuitem>Umetni</guimenuitem> opciju."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Moving a file or subfolder between folders can be done in the same way as "
#~ "copying, except that you choose the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> option "
#~ "or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> instead "
#~ "of <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>. The item that you have "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> will be removed from the original folder "
#~ "when you do the <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> into the new folder."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pomjeranje datoteka ili podfoldera između foldera se može uraditi na isti "
#~ "način kao i kopiranje, osim što onda odabirate <guimenuitem>Isjeci</"
#~ "guimenuitem> opciju ili <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</"
#~ "keycap></keycombo> umjesto <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>. Stavka "
#~ "koju ste <guimenuitem>Isjekli</guimenuitem> će biti uklonjena iz "
#~ "originalnog foldera kada je<guimenuitem>Umetnete</guimenuitem> u novi "
#~ "folder."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can also copy or move selected item(s) to another folder by selecting "
