#~ msgid "Using Drag 'n Drop"
#~ msgstr "Korištenje Povuci i spusti"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&konqueror; also supports Drag and Drop copying and moving of files and "
#~ "folders."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&konqueror; također podržava povuci i spusti kopiranje i pomjeranje "
#~ "fajlova ili foldera."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can do this by having two instances of &konqueror;, one showing the "
#~ "folder you want to copy from, the other showing the target folder. "
#~ "Position the mouse pointer over the item you wish to copy or move, then, "
#~ "holding the &LMB; pressed, <quote>drag</quote> it to a clear space in the "
#~ "target folder. Release the button and you will be presented with a menu "
#~ "choice of <guimenuitem>Copy Here</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move Here</"
#~ "guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Link Here</guimenuitem>. Take care to "
#~ "<quote>drop</quote> the item into an empty area of the target folder view "
#~ "- dropping it on top of a subfolder will copy or move the item into that "
#~ "folder."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ovo možete uraditi pomoću dvije instance &konqueror; jednu koja prikazuje "
#~ "direktorij iz kojeg želite kopirati, drugi u koji želite kopirati. "
#~ "Pozicionirajte pokazivač miša preko stavke koju želite kopirati ili "
#~ "pomjeriti, onda pritisnite &LMB;,  <quote>povuci</quote> je da očistite "
#~ "prostor u odredišnom folderu. Otpustite tipku i pojavit će se meni sa "
#~ "izborom <guimenuitem>Kopiraj ovdje</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Pomjeri "
#~ "ovdje</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Linkuj ovdje</guimenuitem>. Ne "
#~ "zaboravite da  <quote>spustite</quote> stavku  na prazno mjesto u "
#~ "odredišnom folderu-spuštanjem na neki podfolder će kopirati ili pomjeriti "
#~ "stavku u taj folder."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can also set up &konqueror; to show more than one folder within its "
#~ "window and drag &amp; drop between them."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete također podesiti &konqueror; da prikazuje više od jednog foldera "
#~ "unutar svog prozora i povuci &amp; spusti između njih."

#~ msgid "Split Views for Drag &amp; Drop"
