#~ msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
#~ msgstr "Označavanje stavki pomoću miša"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around "
#~ "a group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items "
#~ "in the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
#~ "pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
