#~ "perhaps the best, way of transferring files between computers over the "
#~ "Internet."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&FTP;, ili Protokol za prijenos datoteka, je jedan od najranijih, i još "
#~ "možda najbolji, način  prijenosa datoteka između kompjutera preko "
#~ "interneta."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as "
