#~ msgid "&fsview; - the File System View"
#~ msgstr "&fsview; - the File System View"

#~ msgid "Introduction"
#~ msgstr "Uvod"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The &fsview; Plugin for &konqueror; is another view mode for objects of "
#~ "mimetype <literal>inode/directory</literal> for local files. It can be "
#~ "viewed as an alternative to the various iconviews and listviews for "
#~ "browsing the content of your local file system."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&fsview; dodatak za &konqueror; je još jedan režim pregleda za objekte "
#~ "mime tipa <literal>inode/directory</literal> za lokalne datoteke. Može se "
#~ "smatrati alternativom za različite preglede ikona i listi za "
#~ "pretraživanje sadržaja vašeg sitema lokalnih daoteka."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The unique property of &fsview; is its ability to show whole nested "
#~ "folder hierarchies using a so-called tree map for graphical "
#~ "visualization. Tree maps allow for displaying metrics of objects in "
#~ "nested structures: each object is represented by a rectangle whose area "
#~ "is proportional to its metric. The sum of the children's metrics must be "
#~ "equal to or smaller than the parent object's metric."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Jedinstveno obilježje &fsview; je sposobnost da prikaže cijelu "
#~ "hijerarhiju foldera korištenjem takozvane mape za grafičku vizualizaciju. "
#~ "Mape stabla vam dozvoljavaju da prikažete metriku objekata u strukturama; "
#~ "svaki objekat je predstavljen sa trouglom čija je površina proporcionalna "
#~ "njegovim dimenzijama. Zbir dimenzija djece mora biti jednaka ili manja od "
#~ "dimenzija roditelja."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "For &fsview;, sizes of files and folders are chosen as the metric, where "
#~ "the size of a folder is defined to be the sum of the sizes of its "
#~ "subitems. This way, big files even deep down in the folder hierarchy can "
#~ "be spotted easily be looking for large rectangles. So &fsview; can be "
#~ "looked at as a graphical and interactive version of the &UNIX; "
#~ "<command>du</command> command."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Za &fsview; veličina datoteka i foldera su birani kao dimenzije, gdje je "
#~ "veličina foldera određena da bude zbir veličina svojih podstavki. Na ovaj "
#~ "način, velike datoteke duboko u hijerarhiji foldera mogu biti uočene "
#~ "lakše gledanjem velikih trouglova. &fsview; se može gledati kao grafička "
#~ "i interaktivan verzija &UNIX; <command>du</command>  komande."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The integration of &fsview; as part of Konqueror allows it to use the "
#~ "standard features such as context file menus, and mime type sensitive "
#~ "actions. But it was chosen not to implement automatic update by watching "
#~ "file system changes: if you delete a file shown in &fsview; outside of "
#~ "&konqueror;, you have to update manually by &eg; pressing <keycap>F5</"
#~ "keycap> to see the change. The reason for this decision is the "
#~ "potentially huge number of files which would have to be watched for "
#~ "changes, and thus, could put an unreasonable pressure on system resources "
#~ "for a small feature."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Integracija &fsview; kao dijela Konquerora dozvolja mu da koristi "
#~ "standardne opcije kao konteksne menije, i mime tipove akcija. Ali je "
#~ "izabrano da se ne  ugradi automatsko unapređivanje gledanjem sistemskih "
#~ "promjena: ako izbrišete datoteku  prikazanu u &fsview; izvan &konqueror;, "
#~ "morate unaprijediti ručno sa &eg; pritiskom <keycap>F5</keycap> da vidite "
#~ "promijene. Razlog za ovu odluku je potencionalno veliki broj datoteka "
#~ "koje bi se morale gledati na promjene, i staviti ogromno opterećenje na "
#~ "sistemske resurse za malu opciju."

#~ msgid "Visualization Features"
#~ msgstr "Opcije vizualizacije"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This section explains the graphical visualization of &fsview; in detail."
#~ msgstr "Ova sekcija objašnjava grafičku vizualizaciju u &fsview; u detalje."

#~ msgid "Item Drawing Options"
#~ msgstr "Crtanje stavki opcije"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In &fsview;, an item of the tree map visualization is a rectangle "
#~ "representing a file or folder of your file system. For easier navigation, "
#~ "rectangles have meaningful coloring and labeling options."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "U &fsview;, stavka mape vizuelnog stabla  je trougao koji predstavlja "
#~ "datoteku ili folder vašeg sistema datoteka. Za lakšu navigaciju, "
#~ "trouglovi imaju logične boje i oznake."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The color of a rectangle, switchable via menu item "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Color Mode</guisubmenu></"
#~ "menuchoice> can be either representative of <guimenuitem>Depth</"
#~ "guimenuitem>, for easy detection of nesting, or a color mapping of "
#~ "different file attributes such as name, owner, group, or mime type."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Boja trougla, koja se može mijenjati sa meni stavkom "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Color Mode</guisubmenu></"
#~ "menuchoice> može biti predstavnik <guimenuitem>Depth</guimenuitem> za "
#~ "laše detektovanje gnježdenja , ili mapiranje bojom različitih atributa "
#~ "datoteka kao što su ime, vlasnik, grupa ili mime tip."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A rectangle can be labeled with the various attributes of the "
#~ "corresponding file or folder. For each attribute, you can choose whether "
#~ "it should be shown at all, only if space is available, or if space should "
#~ "be taken from children (thus introducing errors to pure tree map drawing "
#~ "constraints). Additionally, you can choose the relative location of the "
#~ "label in the rectangle."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Trougao se može označiti sa različitim aztributima odgovarajuće datoteke "
#~ "ili foldera. Za svaki atribut, možete odabrati da li će biti prikazan "
#~ "ikako, samo ako je prostor dostupan, ili da li bi prostor trebao biti "
#~ "uzet od djece . Dodatno možete izabrati lokaciju oznake u trouglu."

#~ msgid "TreeMap Drawing Algorithms"
#~ msgstr "Algoritmi za ctranje stablo mape."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "For drawing algorithms in tree maps, the rule that the area is "
#~ "proportional to the metric of an item should hold true. With the tree map "
#~ "in &fsview;, this goal isn't always met: we draw borders to show the "
#~ "nesting of items, and this border takes space for an item which is "
#~ "possibly lost for the areas of child items. Note that less space is lost "
#~ "for the border if the rectangle is quadratic."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Za algoritme crtanja u mapama stabla, pravilo da je prostor "
#~ "proporcionalan dimenzijama stavke bi trebao važiti. Sa mapom stabla u "
#~ "&fsview; ovaj uslov nije uvijek postignut : crtamo granice da prikažemo "
#~ "slaganje stavki, i ova granica zauzima prostor za stavku koja je "
#~ "vjerovatno izgubljena za prostor djece. Manje prostora se gubi ako je "
#~ "trougao kavadratičan."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Similarly, it is better for a good overview to let each rectangle at "
#~ "least have its name as a label. It is an option to always force space for "
#~ "labels, or only to draw labels when empty space is available. In the "
#~ "latter case, the tool tips appearing when the mouse is held over an item "
#~ "can help a lot. They show information for the item the mouse is currently "
#~ "over, together with its parent folders up to the root item of the tree "
#~ "map."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Slično, bolje je za dobar pregled da svaki triugao ima kao labele barem "
#~ "ime. To je opcija za forsiranje mjesta za labele, ili samo za crtanje "
#~ "labela kada je prazan prostor dostupan. U posljednjem slučaju, savjeti u "
#~ "vezi altki koji se pojavljuju kada se miš dovede na stavku mogu biti od "
#~ "pomoći. Oni prikazuju informacije za stavku na koju pokazuje miš, zajedno "
#~ "sa folderom roditelja pa sve do korijena stavke mape stabla."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "How the space of an item is split into subareas for children is left to "
#~ "the implementation. It is always better to try to split areas in such a "
#~ "way that rectangles are as quadratic as possible, both for labeling and "
#~ "less space lost by borders. The best methods in this regard are "
#~ "<guilabel>Rows</guilabel>, <guilabel>Columns</guilabel>, or "
#~ "<guilabel>Recursive Bisection</guilabel>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kako je prostor stavke raspoređen u podprostore za djecu je ostavljeno "
#~ "implementaciji. Uvijek je bolje podijeliti prostor na takav način da su "
#~ "trouglovi kavdratični što je više moguće, za labelovanje i manje je "
#~ "prostora izgubljeno zbog granica. Najbolje metode za ovo su "
#~ "<guilabel>Redovi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Kolone</guilabel>, ili "
#~ "<guilabel>Recursive Bisection</guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can choose the minimal area of items to be drawn via the menu item "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop at Area</"
#~ "guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Instead, a hash pattern will be drawn over the "
#~ "parents area to signal that this space is in fact occupied by a child or "
#~ "children."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete izabrati najmanji prostor stavke koji će biti crtan iz meni stavke "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop at Area</"
#~ "guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Hash obrazac će biti nacrtan preko "
#~ "roditeljskog prostora da označi da je ovaj prostor zauzet od djeteta ili "
#~ "djece."

#~ msgid "User Interface"
#~ msgstr "Korisničko sučelje"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&fsview; supports multiple selection of items, similar to the iconview "
#~ "and listview. This allows for actions to be done simultaneously to a set "
#~ "of files. A simple mouse click always selects a single item below the "
#~ "mouse pointer. Use a mouse click in combination with pressing the &Shift; "
#~ "key for range selection or the &Ctrl; key for selection toggle. Note that "
#~ "by selecting an item, subitems can no longer be selected. Selecting an "
#~ "item will also clear the selection of all its parent items before."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&fsview; podržava višestruki odabir stavki, slično pregledu ikon i "
#~ "pregledu listi. Ovo omogućava da se radnje obavljaju istovremeno na skup "
#~ "datoteka. Klik miša uvije odabira jednu stavku ispod pokazivača miša. "
#~ "Koristite kombinaciju klika miša i pritiska &Shift; tipke za označavanje "
#~ "određenog dometa ili &Ctrl; tipku za toggle odabir. Primjetite da pri "
#~ "odabiru stavke, podstavke ne mogu biti odabrane. Odabirom stavke će "
#~ "također obristi odabir svih roditeljskih stavki odprije."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Keyboard navigation is available in tree maps: use <keycap>Left Arrow</"
#~ "keycap> and <keycap>Right Arrow</keycap> keys to move the current item "
#~ "between siblings, and the <keycap>Up Arrow</keycap> and <keycap>Down "
#~ "Arrow</keycap> keys to go up and down the nesting hierarchy. "
#~ "<keycap>Space</keycap> selects the item; in conjunction with &Shift; does "
#~ "range selection; and with the &Ctrl; key held down simultaneously, "
#~ "toggles selection of the current item. Press <keycap>Return</keycap> to "
#~ "run the open action on the current item."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Navigacija tastaturom je dostupna u mapama stabla: koristite  "
#~ "<keycap>Lijeva strelica</keycap> i <keycap>Desna strelica</keycap> tipku "
#~ "da pomjerate trenutnu stavku između sličnih, <keycap>Gore strelica</"
#~ "keycap> i <keycap>Dole strelica</keycap> tipke da idete gore ili dole "
#~ "kroz hijerarhiju. <keycap>Space</keycap>  odabira stavku, i zajedno sa "
#~ "&Shift; obavlja odabir opsega; i sa &Ctrl; tipkom pritisnutom "
#~ "istovremeno, toggle odabira trenutnu stavku. Pristisnite <keycap>Return</"
#~ "keycap> da pokrenete otvorenu akciju na trenutnoj stavki."

