#~ msgid "View Profiles"
#~ msgstr "Profil pogleda"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&konqueror; can save a whole set of options as a <quote>View Profile</"
#~ "quote>. Some view profiles are part of the standard &konqueror; "
#~ "installation, such as <property>Web Browsing</property>, <property>File "
#~ "Management</property>, <property>KDE Development</property>, "
#~ "<property>Midnight Commander</property> and <property>Tabbed Browsing</"
#~ "property>; but you can add your own, too."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&konqueror; može spasiti cijeli set opcija kao <quote>View Profile</"
#~ "quote>.  Neki profili su dio standardnog &konqueror;.ove instalacije, "
#~ "kao  <property>Web Browsing</property>, <property>File Management</"
#~ "property>, <property>KDE Development</property>, <property>Midnight "
#~ "Commander</property> i <property>Tabbed Browsing</property>; ali možete "
#~ "dodati i vaše također."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To modify a view profile (say, the <property>Web Browsing</property> "
#~ "profile), load the profile with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#~ "guimenu><guisubmenu>Load View Profile</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Web "
#~ "Browsing</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, and change the &konqueror; settings "
#~ "to whatever you want. Now select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#~ "guimenu><guimenuitem>Save View Profile As... </guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
#~ "In the dialog which appears, you can change the name of the profile, "
#~ "which will create a new profile with that name, or you can leave the name "
#~ "as it is to modify the current profile. If you select <guilabel>Save URLs "
#~ "in profile</guilabel>, the current &URL; will be loaded when you load "
#~ "that view profile. This functions in a similar way to the <quote>Home "
#~ "Page</quote> in many web browsers. If you want &konqueror; to start up "
#~ "with an empty window enter <userinput>about:blank</userinput> into the "
#~ "location bar before saving the profile."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Da modifikujete profil (recimo, <property>Veb pretraživanje</property> "
#~ "profil), učitajte profil sa <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
#~ "guimenu><guisubmenu>Učitaj profil pregleda</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Veb "
#~ "pretraživanje</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, i promijenite &konqueror;-ove "
#~ "postavke na šta želite. Sada odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
#~ "guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi profil pregleda kao... </guimenuitem></"
#~ "menuchoice>. U dijalogu koji se pojavi, možete promijeniti ime profila, "
#~ "što će napraviti novi profil sa tim imenom, ili možete otstaviti isto ime "
#~ "i time modifikovati trenutni profil. Ako odaberete <guilabel>Spasi URL u "
#~ "profil</guilabel>, trenutni &URL; će biti učitan kada učitate taj profil. "
#~ "Ovo radi na sličan način kao <quote>Startna stranica</quote> u mnogim veb "
#~ "pretraživačima. Ako želite da &konqueror; počne sa praznim prozorom "
#~ "unesite <userinput>about:blank</userinput> u locatin traku prije "
#~ "spašavanja profila."

#, fuzzy
#~| msgid ""
#~| "You can create a desktop icon to start &konqueror; with your new "
#~| "profile. First create a desktop icon by clicking with the &RMB; onto the "
#~| "&konqueror; entry in the application launcher menu. Then select "
#~| "<guimenuitem>Add to Desktop</guimenuitem> in the context menu. Open the "
#~| "settings dialog of the new icon on your desktop by clicking on the "
#~| "<guiicon>Tools</guiicon> icon. Change <guilabel> Command</guilabel> in "
#~| "the <guilabel>Application</guilabel> tab page to "
#~| "<userinput><command>kfmclient</command> <option>openProfile "
#~| "<replaceable>MyNewProfile</replaceable></option></userinput>, "
#~| "<replaceable>MyNewProfile</replaceable> being what you called the new "
#~| "profile. Then change the name to something like <filename>MyNewProfile</"
#~| "filename> ."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can create a desktop icon in a <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> "
#~ "widget to start &konqueror; with your new profile. First drag and drop "
#~ "the &konqueror; entry in the application launcher menu into a "
#~ "<guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> widget on the desktop or select "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Add to Desktop</guimenuitem> from the contextmenu if your "
#~ "Desktop has a <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> layout. Open the settings "
#~ "dialog of the new icon by selecting <guilabel>Properties</guilabel> from "
#~ "its context menu. Change <guilabel>Command</guilabel> in the "
#~ "<guilabel>Application</guilabel> tab page to "
#~ "<userinput><command>kfmclient</command> <option>openProfile "
#~ "<replaceable>MyNewProfile</replaceable></option></userinput>, "
#~ "<replaceable>MyNewProfile</replaceable> being what you called the new "
#~ "profile. Then change the name to something like <filename>MyNewProfile</"
#~ "filename> ."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete napraviti desktop ikonu da pokrenete &konqueror; sa novim "
#~ "profilom. Prvo napravite desktop ikonu desnim klikom miša; na &konqueror; "
#~ "u meniju aplikacija. Onda odaberite <guimenuitem>Dodaj na  Desktop</"
#~ "guimenuitem> u konteksnom meniju. Otvorite dijalog postavki nove ikone na "
#~ "vašem desktopu klikom na <guiicon>Alati</guiicon> ikonu. Promijenite "
#~ "<guilabel> Komanda</guilabel> u <guilabel>Aplikacija</guilabel> kartici "
#~ "na <userinput><command>kfmclient</command> <option>openProfile "
#~ "<replaceable>MojNoviProfil</replaceable></option></userinput>, "
#~ "<replaceable>MojNoviProfil</replaceable>kako ste nazvali vaš novi profil. "
#~ "Onda promijenite ime na nešto poput <filename>MojNoviProfil</filename> ."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This screenshot does not show the optional <link linkend=\"sidebar\"> "
#~ "Sidebar</link>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ova slika ekrana ne prikazuje opcionalni <link linkend=\"sidebar\"> Bočna "
#~ "traka</link>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link> can also help you find your "
#~ "way around the file system."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<link linkend=\"sidebar\">Bočna traka</link> vam također može pomoći da "
#~ "se snađete oko fajlova kroz sistem."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The history of recently visited &URL;s that &konqueror; uses for the Text "
#~ "Completion function can be viewed and edited in the <guilabel>History </"
#~ "guilabel> page of the <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Historija nedavno posjećenih &URL;-ova koje &konqueror; koristi za "
#~ "popunjavanje teksta se može pregledati i izmjeniti u <guilabel>Historija</"
#~ "guilabel> stranici <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Bočna traka</link>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can also access your bookmarks from the <link linkend=\"sidebar\"> "
#~ "<guilabel>Sidebar</guilabel></link> or from the <guilabel>Bookmark "
#~ "Toolbar</guilabel>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Također možete pristupiti vašim oznakama iz  <link linkend=\"sidebar\"> "
#~ "<guilabel>Bočna traka</guilabel></link> ili iz <guilabel>Alatna traka "
#~ "zabilješki</guilabel>."

#~ msgid "The Sidebar"
#~ msgstr "Bočna traka"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Sidebar appears as a separate view at the left of &konqueror;'s "
#~ "window. It can be invoked with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings </"
#~ "guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Sidebar</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or toggled "
#~ "on and off with the <keycap>F9</keycap> key."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Bočna traka se pojavljuje kao odvojeni pregled na lijevoj strani "
#~ "&konqueror;.ovog prozora. Može se pozvati sa "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži bočnu traku</"
#~ "guimenuitem></menuchoice> ili  uključen ili isključen sa  <keycap>F9</"
#~ "keycap> tipkom."

#~ msgid "With the Sidebar"
#~ msgstr "Sa sidebarom"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "It contains a number of tabbed pages; <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
#~ "click on a tab's icon to view that page. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> "
#~ "clicking on the icon for the visible page will collapse the Sidebar so "
#~ "that only the tab icons are visible."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Sadrži nekoliko kartičnih stranica; <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> "
#~ "klik na ikonu kartice da vidite tu stranicu. <mousebutton>Lijevi</"
#~ "mousebutton> klik na ikonu za vidljivu stranicu će suziti bočnu traku "
#~ "tako da su samo ikone kartica vidljive."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This page shows a tree view of your Bookmarks. <mousebutton> Left</"
#~ "mousebutton> click on an item to open it in the main view."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ova stranica prikazuje tree pregled vaših oznaka. <mousebutton> Lijevi</"
#~ "mousebutton> klik na stavku da je otvorite u glavni pregled."

#~ msgid "History"
#~ msgstr "Historija"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This page shows a tree view of your browsing History. <mousebutton>Left</"
#~ "mousebutton> clicking on an item will open it in the main view, or you "
#~ "can open it in a new &konqueror; window by <mousebutton>right </"
#~ "mousebutton> clicking and selecting <guimenuitem>Open in New Window</"
#~ "guimenuitem> from the pop up menu."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ova stranica prikazuje tree pregled vaše historije pretraživanja. "
#~ "<mousebutton>Lijevi</mousebutton> klik na stavku će otvoriti glavni "
#~ "pregled, ili ga možete otvoriti u novom &konqueror;-ovom prozoru sa "
#~ "<mousebutton>desnim </mousebutton>  klikom i odabirom <guimenuitem>Otvori "
#~ "u novom prozoru</guimenuitem> iz skočnog menija."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can remove an item from the history by <mousebutton>right </"
#~ "mousebutton> clicking on it and selecting <guimenuitem>Remove Entry</"
#~ "guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Clear History</guimenuitem> will "
#~ "clear out the entire history."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete ukloniti stavku iz historije sa <mousebutton>desnim </mousebutton> "
#~ "klikom na nju i odabirom <guimenuitem>Ukloni unos</guimenuitem>. Odabirom "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Očisti Historiju</guimenuitem> će ukloniti svu historiju."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The pop up menu you get when you <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click "
#~ "on any entry in the History page also gives you the option of choosing "
#~ "whether the entire history is sorted by name or by date."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Skočni meni koji dobijete kada kliknete<mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> "
#~ "klikom miša na  unos ili stranicu historije vam također daje opciju "
#~ "izbora da li je historija poredana po imenu ili datumu."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Selecting <guimenuitem>Preferences...</guimenuitem> from this pop up menu "
#~ "brings up the <guilabel>History Sidebar</guilabel> control module. This "
#~ "can be used to set the maximum size of your history and set a time after "
#~ "which items are automatically removed. You can also set different fonts "
#~ "for new and old &URL;s. The <guilabel>Detailed tooltips</guilabel> "
#~ "checkbox controls how much information is displayed when you hover the "
#~ "mouse pointer over an item in the history page."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Odabirom <guimenuitem>Postavke...</guimenuitem> iz ovog skočnog menija "
#~ "prikazuje  <guilabel>Bočna traka istorijata</guilabel> kontrolni modul. "
#~ "Ovim se može postaviti maksimalna veličina vaše historije i postaviti "
#~ "vrijeme nakon kojeg su stavke automatski uklonjene. Također možete "
#~ "postaviti različite fontove za nove i stare &URL;-ove.  "
#~ "<guilabel>Detaljni savjeti za alate</guilabel> oznaka kontrolira koliko "
#~ "je informacija prikazano kad dovedete pokazivač miša preko stavke u "
#~ "stranici historije."

#~ msgid "Home Folder"
#~ msgstr "Početni folder"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This page shows a tree view of the subfolders of your home folder. Note "
#~ "that <quote>hidden</quote> folders (those with names beginning with a "
#~ "dot) are not shown. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an item to "
#~ "open it in the main view, or <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click to "
#~ "display a pop up menu allowing you to open the subfolder in a new window "
#~ "or as a new tab page of the main view."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ova stranica prikazuje tree pogled podfoldera vašeh početnog foldera. "
#~ "Primjetite da <quote>skriveni</quote> folderi(oni čije ime počinje sa "
#~ "tačkom) nisu prikazani. <mousebutton>Lijevi</mousebutton> klik na stavku "
#~ "da je otvorite u glavnom pregledu, ili <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> "
#~ "klik da prikažete skočni meni koji vam dozvoljava da otvorite podfolder u "
#~ "novom prozoru ili kao novu karticu glavnog pregleda."

#~ msgid "Network"
#~ msgstr "Mreža"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This page is intended to show a tree view of your important network "
#~ "connections, although local folders can also be included. Again, you can "
#~ "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on an item to open it in the main "
#~ "view or <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click to bring up a menu with a "
#~ "wider range of possibilities."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ova stranica je namjenjena da prikaže tree pogled vaših važnih mrežnih "
#~ "konekcija, iako lokalni folderi mogu biti također uključeni. Ponovo, "
#~ "možete <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik na stavku da je otvorite u "
#~ "glavnom pregledu ili <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> klik da prikažete "
#~ "meni sa više mogućnosti."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The folders shown in the <guilabel>Network</guilabel> page are held in "
#~ "the folder <filename class=\"directory\"> ~/.kde/share/apps/"
#~ "konqsidebartng/virtual_folders/remote/</filename>, and you can make new "
#~ "ones just as you would make any other subfolder. The items within these "
#~ "folders are held as <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files "
#~ "and can be created with &konqueror;'s <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Create New</"
#~ "guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Link to Location (URL)...</guimenuitem></"
#~ "menuchoice> option in the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Folderi prikazani u  <guilabel>Mreža</guilabel> stranici su držani u "
#~ "folderu <filename class=\"directory\"> ~/.kde/share/apps/konqsidebartng/"
#~ "virtual_folders/remote/</filename>, i možete napraviti nove kao što biste "
#~ "napravili bilo koji drugi podfolder. Stavke unutar ovih foldera su držani "
#~ "kao <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> datoteke i mogu biti "
#~ "kreirani sa &konqueror;-om<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Napravi novu</"
#~ "guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Vezu do lokacije (URL)...</guimenuitem></"
#~ "menuchoice> opcijom u <guimenu>Izmjeni</guimenu> meniju."

#~ msgid "Root Folder"
#~ msgstr "Korijenski folder"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Root Folder</guilabel> tree has the path <filename class="
