#~ msgid ""
#~ "To see what Web Shortcuts are available, and perhaps add your own, use "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror..."
#~ "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and open the <guilabel>Web Shortcuts</"
#~ "guilabel> page."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Da vidite koje veb prečice su dostupne, i možda dodate svoje, koristite "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Podesite Konqueror..."
#~ "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> i otvorite <guilabel>Veb prečice</guilabel> "
#~ "stranicu."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Once there, to make a new Web Shortcut select <guibutton>New...</"
#~ "guibutton> and you will now have a new dialog requesting the options and "
#~ "specifications of your new Web Shortcut. The first field is for the human "
#~ "readable name of the search provider; that is, simply the name of the "
#~ "Search provider. For example, <trademark>Google</trademark>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kada ste tamo, da napravite novu veb prečicu odaberite <guibutton>Nova..."
#~ "</guibutton> i sada ćete imati novi dijalog koji zahtjeva opcije i "
#~ "specifikacije za vašu novu veb prečicu. Prvo polje je za ime providera "
#~ "pretrage; to je, samo ime providera pretrage. Na primjer,"
#~ "<trademark>Google</trademark>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the next field you should enter the &URI; that is used to do a search "
#~ "on the search engine. The whole text to be searched for can be specified "
#~ "as <userinput>\\{@}</userinput> or <userinput>\\{0}</userinput>. The "
#~ "recommended version is <userinput>\\{@}</userinput> since it removes all "
#~ "query variables (<replaceable>name</replaceable>=<replaceable>value</"
#~ "replaceable>) from the resulting string whereas <userinput>\\{0}</"
#~ "userinput> will be substituted with the unmodified query string."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "U sljedećem polju unesite &URL; koji se koristi da obavi pretragu u "
#~ "pretraživaču. Cijeli tekst koji se pretražuje se može specificirati kao  "
#~ "<userinput>\\{@}</userinput> ili <userinput>\\{0}</userinput>. "
#~ "Preporučena verzija je <userinput>\\{@}</userinput> zato što uklanja sve "
#~ "varijable upita (<replaceable>ime</replaceable>=<replaceable>vrijednost</"
#~ "replaceable>) iz stringa rezultata dok <userinput>\\{0}</userinput>  će "
#~ "biti zamijenjen sa ne promijenjenim stringom upita."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can use <userinput>\\{1}</userinput> ... <userinput>\\{n}</userinput> "
#~ "to specify certain words from the query and <userinput>"
#~ "\\{<varname><replaceable>name</replaceable></varname>}</userinput> to "
#~ "specify a value given by <userinput><varname><replaceable>name</"
#~ "replaceable></varname>=<replaceable>value</replaceable></userinput> in "
#~ "the user query. In addition it is possible to specify multiple references "
#~ "(names, numbers and strings) at once, like "
#~ "<userinput>(\\{<varname><replaceable>name1</replaceable></varname>,"
#~ "<varname><replaceable>name2</replaceable></varname>,...,"
#~ "\"<replaceable>string</replaceable>\"})</userinput>. The first matching "
#~ "value (from the left) will be used as substitution value for the "
#~ "resulting &URI;. A quoted string can be used as the default value if "
#~ "nothing matches from the left of the reference list."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Možete koristiti <userinput>\\{1}</userinput> ... <userinput>\\{n}</"
#~ "userinput> da specificirate određene riječi iz upita i <userinput>"
#~ "\\{<varname><replaceable>ime</replaceable></varname>}</userinput> da "
#~ "specificirate vrijednost datu od <userinput><varname><replaceable>ime</"
#~ "replaceable></varname>=<replaceable>vrijednost</replaceable></userinput> "
#~ "odjednom, kao <userinput>(\\{<varname><replaceable>ime1</replaceable></"
#~ "varname>,<varname><replaceable>ime2</replaceable></varname>,...,"
#~ "\"<replaceable>string</replaceable>\"})</userinput>. Prva podudarna "
#~ "vrijednost (Sa lijeva) će biti iskorištena kao zamijenska vrijednost za "
#~ "rezultujući &URI;. Označeni niz znakova može biti korišten kao zadana "
#~ "vrijednost ako ništa nije podudarno sa lijeva od referentne liste."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To make a basic Web Shortcut here however, all that is required is the "
#~ "&URI; that is used to do a search on the search engine. Following our "
#~ "previous example with <trademark>Google</trademark>, we would enter "
#~ "<userinput>http://www.google.com/search?q=\\{@}&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;"
#~ "oe=UTF-8</userinput>. You can often easily find where to place the "
#~ "<userinput>\\{@}</userinput> by doing a search on the search engine in "
#~ "question, and then analyzing the &URL; address. For example, doing a "
#~ "<trademark>Google</trademark> search for &konqueror; produces the &URL;: "
#~ "<ulink url=\"http://www.google.com/search?q=konqueror&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;"
#~ "oe=UTF-8\">http://www.google.com/search?q=konqueror&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;"
#~ "oe=UTF-8</ulink>. Now you need to merely replace &konqueror; with "
#~ "<userinput>\\{@}</userinput> in this example to find the appropriate "
#~ "&URI; to be entered."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Da napravite prostu veb prečicu ovdje, sve što je potrebno je &URI; koji "
#~ "se koristi da pretražuje u pretraživaču. Prateći prethodni primjer sa "
#~ "<trademark>Google</trademark>, unijeli bismo <userinput>http://www.google."
#~ "com/search?q=\\{@}&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;oe=UTF-8</userinput>. Često možete "
#~ "lahko naći gdje da stavite <userinput>\\{@}</userinput> obavljanjem "
#~ "pretrage u pitanju, i onda analizom &URL; adrese. Na primjer, obavljanjem "
#~ "<trademark>Google</trademark> pretrahe za &konqueror; kreira &URL;: "
#~ "<ulink url=\"http://www.google.com/search?q=konqueror&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;"
#~ "oe=UTF-8\">http://www.google.com/search?q=konqueror&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;"
#~ "oe=UTF-8</ulink>. Sada samo treba zamijeniti &konqueror; sa <userinput>"
#~ "\\{@}</userinput> u ovom primjeru da pronađete odgovarajući &URI; koji "
#~ "treba biti unesen."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the third field you need to enter the &URI; shortcut. For example, the "
#~ "<userinput>gg</userinput> in <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput>. In the "
#~ "next option &mdash; the drop-down menu &mdash; you have the option to "
#~ "select the character set that will be used to encode the search query. "
#~ "Once you have entered all the options correctly to your satisfaction, "
#~ "press &Enter; and your new Web Shortcut should now be available in "
#~ "&konqueror;."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "U trećem polju trebate unijeti &URI; kratice. Na primjer, <userinput>gg</"
#~ "userinput> u <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput>. U sljedećoj opciji "
#~ "&mdash; padajući meniji &mdash; imate mogućnost da označite set znakova "
#~ "koji će biti korišteni da kodiraju upit pretrage. Kada ste unijeli sve "
#~ "opcije tačno kako ste htjeli, pritisnite &Enter; i vaša nova veb prečica "
#~ "bi trebala biti dostupna u &konqueror;-u."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Install the <guilabel>UserAgent Changer</guilabel> extension from the "
#~ "&konqueror; Plugins and enable it in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#~ "guimenu><guimenuitem> Configure Extensions</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
#~ "This extension adds a <guimenuitem>Change Browser Identification</"
#~ "guimenuitem> item to the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu. Using this item "
#~ "lets you quickly switch between different <quote>User Agent</quote> "
#~ "strings."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Instalirajte  <guilabel>UserAgent Changer</guilabel> ekstenziju iz "
#~ "&konqueror;-a dodataka i uključite je u <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
#~ "guimenu><guimenuitem> Podesite Ekstenzije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ova "
#~ "ekstenzija dodaje <guimenuitem>Promijeni identifikaciju preglednika</"
#~ "guimenuitem> stavku u <guimenu>Alatni</guimenu> meni. Korištenjem ove "
#~ "stavke omogućava vam brže premještanje između različitih <quote>User "
#~ "Agent</quote>."

